high_descs: Turn right, hang a right at the couch and turn left at the coffee table to face the couch.
Pick up the remote control on the far right side on the cushion of the couch.
Turn around, hang a left at the coffee table, take a right at the chair and face the next chair on the left.
Put the remote control on the left side of the chair near the edge.
anns.task_desc: Place a remote control on a chair.

high_descs: Make a right to walk to the longest grey couch.
Pick up the remote on the grey couch that is the farthest on the right side.
Make a right to walk to the grey armchair that is on the right of the other grey armchair.
Set the remote down on the seat of the grey armchair.
anns.task_desc: Move a remote from the grey couch to a grey armchair.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the right of the large grey sofa with the remotes on it
Pick up the remote on the far right side of the sofa
Carry the remote to the grey chair to the right of the sofa
Place the remote on top of the chair
anns.task_desc: Move a remote to the chair
